    "Html": "<p>Hello DCherubini,</p>\r\n<p>You are correct, the resourcewrapper class is not found !!</p>\r\n<p>The Risk project contains the <strong>app.xaml</strong> which contains that last posted merged directory above. The <strong>Style.xaml</strong> aslo and The <strong>Resourcewrapper Class</strong> are within the same project as well.</p>\r\n<p>The resource (.resx) files are all in a separate following project (Risk.Infra).</p>\r\n<p>Have a look at this image that describes the structure layout more clearly.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://skydrive.live.com/redir?resid=B7C7E0C3F0481483!120\">https://skydrive.live.com/redir?resid=B7C7E0C3F0481483!120</a></p>\r\n<p>Best regards</p>",
